 Mṛtyudaṇḍa  : m.: Missile of the god of Death. [See  Daṇḍa ] <br><br><br>_______________________________<br>*5th word in left half of page p129  (+offset) in original book.

06)  मोहनास्त्र|मोहनास्त्र|mohanaastra|మోహనాస్త్ర|ಮೋಹನಾಸ್ತ್ರ|p129
 Mohanāstra  : nt.: Name of a missile. [See  Pramohanāstra ]<br><br><br>_______________________________<br>*1st word in right half of page p129  (+offset) in original book.

