 Brahmopanisad  : f.: Name of a text (?) (or ‘a secret doctrine related to brahman’ ?) <br><br>  At the end of the war, Dhṛtarāṣṭra, when he met the sage Vyāsa, learnt it, along with the duties of a king 15. 43. 2-3 (sa rājā rājadharmāṁś ca brahmopaniṣadaṁ tathā/ avāptavān naraśreṣṭhaḥ…dhṛtarāṣṭraḥ samāsādya vyāsaṁ cāpi tapasvinam//).<br><br><br>_______________________________<br>*3rd word in right half of page p192  (+offset) in original book.<br><br> previous_page p191       next_page p193

