alaḥ) attains heaven 13. 26. 65; one who listens to it when recited obtains birth in the best family and remembers his previous life (jātiṁ ca saṁsmaret) 13. 26. 66.<br><br>  p. 192. 2 before the entry  Bṛhaspatimata  add following entry:<br><br><br>_______________________________<br>*2nd word in left half of page p227  (+offset) in original book.

