 Pauṣa  : m.: Name of a month<br><br>  Aṅgiras had told Bhīṣma that if one spent the month of Pauṣa eating only once a day (bhaktenaikena yaḥ kṣapet) he was born fortunate, handsome and famous 13. 109. 19.<br><br><br>_______________________________<br>*1st word in left half of page p259  (+offset) in original book.

