 Ṛṣyamūka  : m.: See  Ṛśyamūka. <br><br><br>_______________________________<br>*1st word in left half of page p302  (+offset) in original book.

02)  एकपर्वतक|एकपर्वतक|ekaparvataka|ఏకపర్వతక|ಏಕಪರ್ವತಕ|p302
 Ekaparvataka  : m.: Name of a mountain.<br><br>  Kṛṣṇa, Bhīma and Arjuna, while proceeding to Magadha, crossed the rivers flowing near the mountain Ekaparvataka 2. 18. 27.<br><br><br>_______________________________<br>*2nd word in left half of page p302  (+offset) in original book.

