 Nāgasabha  : m.: Name of a mountain.<br><br>  Pāṇḍu, on his way to the Śataśṛṅga mountain with his two wives, first reached the mountain Nāgasabha 1. 110. 42.<br><br><br>_______________________________<br>*2nd word in right half of page p374  (+offset) in original book.

