 Pravarā  : f.: Name of a river.<br><br>  Listed by Saṁjaya among the rivers of the Bhāratavarṣa; people use its water for drinking 6. 10. 22, 13 (for other details see  Palāśinī ).<br><br><br>_______________________________<br>*1st word in right half of page p391  (+offset) in original book.

