08)  सोमतीर्थ^1|सोमतीर्थ|somatiirtha|somateertha|సోమతీర్థ|ಸೋಮತೀರ್ಥ|p483
 Somatīrtha^1  : nt.: Name of a tīrtha.<br><br>  On the river Jayantī (in Kurukṣetra 3. 81. 2); by bathing in it one gets the fruit of a Rājasūya 3. 81. 16.<br><br><br>_______________________________<br>*2nd word in right half of page p483  (+offset) in original book.

