 Kañcya  : m. (pl.): Name of a people.<br><br>  Listed by Ulūka among those warriors who joined the army of Duryodhana (rājacamūṁ sametām/…draviḍāndhrakāñcyaiḥ) 5. 158. 19-20.<br><br><br>_______________________________<br>*4th word in right half of page p652  (+offset) in original book.

